high_descs: Turn around and walk to the end of the kitchen counter, then turn left and proceed to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon that is inside the sink.
Turn back around and walk to the far edge of the kitchen counter and turn right, then walk to the yellow chair at the left end of the counter.
Place the spoon in the fry pan on the counter, between the lettuce and the bread.
Pick up the fry pan with the spoon inside it from the counter.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the counter, then turn left again and walk back to the sink.
Place the fry pan with the spoon inside it in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a fry pan with a spoon inside it, in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight to the door, then turn left until you reach the kitchen counter top with the sink
pick up the spoon inside the sink
walk to the window on the opposite wall, then turn right and proceed straight to the door. Once at the door, turn to face the counter top
place the spoon on the plate to the right of the bread
pick up the spoon while it is on the plate
move around the counter, then turn left, followed by a right so you can face the sink
place the spoon and plate in the sink
anns.task_desc: Bring a clean spoon to a plate for use, empty both the plate and spoon in the sink

high_descs: Move to the sink to the left of the fridge
Pick up a spoon from the sink
Move to the counter to the left of the stove around the counter
Place the spoon on a plate on the counter
Pick up the plate with the spoon from the counter
Move to the sink to the left of the fridge
Place the plate in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a fork inside the sink.
